    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your<strong> mince</strong> (remove the paper if required!)<strong> </strong>and cook for 4-6 min or until browned and starting to caramelise, breaking it up with a wooden spoon as you go</p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/satay-lean-pork-rice-with-pickled-cucumber-salad/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, boil half a kettle</p><p>Peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>ginger</strong></p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/satay-lean-pork-rice-with-pickled-cucumber-salad/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>peanut butter</strong>, <strong>red</strong> <strong>chilli relish</strong>, 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong> and 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[2 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[3 tbsp]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>in a bowl</p><p>Add your <strong>soy sauce</strong> and the juice of <strong>half</strong> your <strong>lime[s]</strong> and give everything a good mix up<strong> </strong>\u2013 this is your <strong>satay sauce</strong></p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>lime</strong> into 1 wedge per person</p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/satay-lean-pork-rice-with-pickled-cucumber-salad/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once the mince has browned, add the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>ginger</strong> and cook for 1-2 min or until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, add your<strong> stock mix </strong>to the pan</p><p>Add your <strong>basmati rice</strong> with 300ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[390ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[600ml]</span> <strong>cold water</strong> to the pan and bring to the boil</p><p>Cover with a lid, reduce the heat to low and cook for 10-12 min or until the water is absorbed, the rice is cooked and the mince is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/satay-lean-pork-rice-with-pickled-cucumber-salad/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, halve your <strong>cucumber</strong> lengthways then scrape out the seeds using a teaspoon, discard the seeds</p><p>Slice the <strong>cucumber halves</strong> finely</p><p>Trim, then slice your <strong>spring onion[s]</strong> finely</p><p>Top, tail and slice your <strong>radishes</strong> (as finely as you can)</p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/satay-lean-pork-rice-with-pickled-cucumber-salad/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> sliced cucumber</strong>,<strong> sliced radish </strong>and <strong>spring onion</strong> to a bowl</p><p>Add your <strong>rice vinegar</strong> and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Mix well and set aside to pickle \u2013 this is your <strong>pickled cucumber & radish salad</strong></p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/satay-lean-pork-rice-with-pickled-cucumber-salad/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Strip your <strong>mint leaves</strong> from their stems and chop them finely, discard the stems</p><p>Chop your <strong>coriander</strong> finely, including the stems</p><p>Chop your<strong> roasted peanuts </strong>roughly</p><p>Once the rice is cooked, stir through the <strong>chopped mint leaves</strong>, <strong>coriander</strong> and <strong>peanuts</strong> \u2013 this is your <strong>mince rice</strong></p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/satay-lean-pork-rice-with-pickled-cucumber-salad/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>lean pork rice</strong> with the <strong>pickled cucumber & radish salad </strong>to the side</p><p>Drizzle with the <strong>satay sauce</strong></p><p>Garnish with a <strong>lime wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
